==Description==
Bob is one of the most unfriendly grobos living in [[Citadel Island]]. He likes patrolling the western part of [[Lupin-Burg]], usually for no visible reason.
Bob has a little brother, studying at the [[school]] of Citadel Island.

==Role in Twinsen's adventure==
Like most characters, Bob's only role in [[Twinsen]]'s adventure was to give hints. In his case, it was a hint about what happend to [[Raph]], the [[lighthouse]] keeper.

